hose sound follows a magnetic path; within his life's story, how many subsections are delineated under \"Life and career\"?\n\n16. From the counts you extracted for the last artist, discover how many 1-bits illuminate the binary form of that number in clue 15.\n\n17. Finally, compute: the absolute difference between the elevation from clue 9 and the Google score from clue 12, then take that result modulo 10. What single digit do you uncover from clue 9, clue 12, clue 15, and clue 16?",
